drm/i915/dg1: add hpd interrupt handling

DG1 has one more combo phy port, no TC and all irq handling goes through
SDE, like for MCC.

v2: Also change intel_hpd_pin_default() to include DG1 mapping
v3, v4: Rebase on hpd refactor

